    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>/authors/admin/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/authors/admin/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I am currently a Ph.D. candidate in Penn State&#39;s College of Nursing with research focus on contructing inclusive healthcare ecology for people with disabilities and their family caregivers. To be a pragmatic research and nurse data scientist, I am working to generate scientific evidence through data-driven research and utilize this evidence for designing high-quality healthcare interventions for the visually impaired population. I have used diverse research methods to conduct bibliometric studies of published articles on particular research topics, discover latent topics from a large amount of text data, and develop predictive models by using machine learning algorithms. All of my academic accomplishments came from my family (JooYoung and Arang)&amp;lsquo;s support.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
